{"about_the_game":"In this prologue to <i>Security: The Horrible Nights</i>, you take on the role of a security guard at a hospital. From your small office, your job is to watch the entire hospital through security cameras. If you see a problem, you must run out and fix it!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199440/extras/security_guy_box_transparent_five_times_as_big.png?t=1728391925\" />  <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199440/extras/security_guy_box_transparent_five_times_as_big.png?t=1728391925\" />  <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199440/extras/security_guy_sucked_into_bin.gif?t=1728391925\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199440/extras/security_guy_box_transparent_five_times_as_big.png?t=1728391925\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199440/extras/security_guy_killed_by_depression.gif?t=1728391925\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199440/extras/security_guy_box_transparent_five_times_as_big.png?t=1728391925\" /> <br><br>You can fix nearly every problem by pointing your flashlight at it and yell! But some problems can be deadly, so you have to be careful if you want to survive all the stories in this anthology horror game.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199440/extras/security_guy_box_transparent_five_times_as_big.png?t=1728391925\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199440/extras/angel_idle.gif?t=1728391925\" />  <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199440/extras/security_guy_drinks_coffee_2.gif?t=1728391925\" /><br><br>All the stories are based on fan-submitted ideas. It is still possible to get your idea included in a free DLC for the main game if you visit the <i>Security: The Horrible Nights</i> Steam page. There is a thread called: &quot;Make a Story for the Game.&quot;<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199440/extras/security_guy_box_transparent_five_times_as_big.png?t=1728391925\" />  <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199440/extras/security_guy_box_transparent_five_times_as_big.png?t=1728391925\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199440/extras/security_guy_box_transparent_five_times_as_big.png?t=1728391925\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199440/extras/cat_wash.gif?t=1728391925\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199440/extras/security_guy_box_transparent_five_times_as_big.png?t=1728391925\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199440/extras/doubleganger_stabs_patient.gif?t=1728391925\" /><br><br>You get 4 unique stories based on fan ideas. You will encounter ghosts, monsters, and other horrible beings while trying to keep the hospital safe.<br><br>The main game,<i> Security: The Horrible Nights</i>, will be released later in 2024.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199440/extras/security_guy_box_transparent_five_times_as_big.png?t=1728391925\" />  <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199440/extras/security_guy_box_transparent_five_times_as_big.png?t=1728391925\" />  <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.c